FBIS4-21951 "jptot015__l94116" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 8 April 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY `Terrorists' Burn 20 Houses in Diyarbakir, No Casualties `Terrorists' Burn 20 Houses in Diyarbakir, No Casualties TA0804164594 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1500 GMT 8 Apr 94 TA0804164594 Ankara TRT Television Network Turkish BFN [Announcer-read report] [Text] Terrorists raided the Tur village in Islamkoy in Kulp District in Diyarbakir last night and set 20 houses on fire. There were no casualties. The houses are no longer habitable. Unal Erkan, governor of the state of emergency region, went to Tur after the incident. Our correspondent reports from the site of the incident that the citizens whose houses were burned down have been supplied with food and blankets as a first measure.
